{"tid":2453632,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［警世］買野真係唔好偷平$450 1set數碼暴龍之伏","createTime":"2021-03-19T14:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T15:22:17.000Z","uid":195924,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5ada421531c62340619652e219febba63b016f43","tid":2453632,"uid":195924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:51:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的有一日熄爐有條友同我講$450 一set數碼暴龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入面有戰鬥暴龍、鋼鐵鳩露露同奧米加。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即時聽到扯旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後二話不說pm條fb友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾撚錢等左幾日都未有貨已經覺得伏伏地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後朋友話返俾我知果個fb page block鳩左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n送上圖幾張以防大家中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錢預左冇了 買左個教訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係買野勿貪平<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CuqdKx4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCuqdKx4.png&h=c1644947&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mGnvMMq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmGnvMMq.png&h=206d0aaf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1YWwwc6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1YWwwc6.jpg&h=405ba10a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d8d9086a5442a26ad93f8a0109070e7fa6378da","tid":2453632,"uid":139173,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:51:52.000Z","msg":"原來會有人喺Facebook買嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb629432452ae3f99748